# Estratégia de Testes — {NOME_DO_PROJETO}

## Stack

- **Unit/Integration:** Vitest + React Testing Library
- **E2E:** Playwright
- **Contratos:** Zod
- **A11y:** axe-core (`@axe-core/playwright`)
- **Coverage:** v8

## Comandos

```bash
bun test                 # unit + integration
bun test --coverage      # com cobertura
bunx playwright test     # E2E
bunx playwright test --ui
bun run scripts/check-test-health.mjs
```

## Metas de cobertura (por risco)

| Domínio | Meta linhas | Camadas obrigatórias |
|---|---|---|
| Auth | 90% | unit + integration + E2E + RLS |
| Pagamento | 95% | unit + contract + E2E |
| CRUD principal | 80% | unit + integration + E2E happy path |
| UI marketing | smoke | E2E opcional |

